posts.post_title: FS: RPPCs minor league - Kentucky - T210 connection
posts.post_content:
I've had these awhile and never made much headway on identifying them - 

The light-colored jersey seems to say "Winchester" and the other two have a "W, " although in a different font.  The only Winchester team in BB Ref was in Kentucky and existed from 1908-1924 in the Blue Grass League.  T210 Series 6 Old Mill features this league and team.  These guys could be part of the set - 

Here's a previous thread:
[url]https://www.net54baseball.com/showthread.php?t=283721[/url]

I'm happy to let these go to a collector of T210s or other related material. Let me know if you're interested, or make an offer - 

Tim
